  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>A core component of the <fr:link href="/NZZ7/" title="TPU Architecture" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/NZZ7/" display-uri="NZZ7" type="local">TPU architecture</fr:link> responsible for elementwise operations.</html:p>
    <html:ul><html:li>2D <fr:link href="/Q7ZD/" title="Vector ISA / SIMD" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/Q7ZD/" display-uri="Q7ZD" type="local">SIMD</fr:link> execution, where each of 1024 <html:em>sites</html:em> execute same program in lockstep.</html:li>
  <html:li>Each site contains 4 ALUs, enabling 4096 FLOPs.</html:li>
  <html:li>Fed a 8x128 <fr:link href="https://kellenkanarios.com/OGCRO/" type="external">Vector Register</fr:link> in one cycle.</html:li></html:ul>
  </fr:mainmatter>
