              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>A core component of the <fr:link href="/NZZ7/" title="TPU Architecture" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/NZZ7/" display-uri="NZZ7" type="local">TPU architecture</fr:link> responsible for performing matrix multiplication via a <html:em>systolic array</html:em>.</html:p>
                <html:ul><html:li>256x256 totaling 65,536 <html:em>multiply accumulate</html:em> units i.e. each unit can multiply and add in one cycle.</html:li>
  
 <html:div class="jms-callout" style="
  margin: 1em 0 1em 0.25em;
